Was Irradiated 10 Minutes at Density Beam is 1.08E+12
Protons/Cm**2.Sec. Another Target was Irradiated 1 Hour
First Measurement has Been Executed After 50
Minutes After Irradiation. Each Target was Measured 65
Times During to 5 Months After Irradiations.
This is Weighted Average For Two Intependent
Flags and Misc-Col are Added to Data-Section.
